Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.54,0:23:53.60,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}Really，you are easy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.70,0:24:02.18,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}怒りたくもなるのわ　You know
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.29,0:22:41.47,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}1　2
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.66,0:22:42.93,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}1　2　3　4
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.07,0:23:02.18,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}剛才起你就很在意那個女學生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.29,0:23:06.84,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}這點小事哪裡瞞得過我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.97,0:23:12.09,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}明明有我在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.20,0:23:16.06,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}你這究竟是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.25,0:23:22.09,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}別以為我會像這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.22,0:23:25.82,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}永遠陪伴在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.94,0:23:27.78,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}要知道總有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.86,0:23:31.86,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}一定會有某個人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.97,0:23:36.33,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}將我從你的身邊奪走
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.91,0:23:41.56,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}到時再後悔已經遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.68,0:23:46.72,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}到時再痛哭也無濟於事了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.96,0:23:51.41,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}就算露出那種表情也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.54,0:23:53.60,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}Really，you are easy
